# Macrio

Open-source (AGPL-3.0) food & fitness tracker. **v1.0 = food logging + EU-14 allergens.** Bilingual UI (nl/en). Stack: **Expo (React Native, TypeScript)** + **Supabase (Postgres, RLS, Auth, Storage)**.

